QUESTION NO: 1
Which of the following statement regarding MIP insertion is correct?
A. You can add channels to the multiplex after MIP insertion
B. You can add stuffing after the MIP insertion
C. You cannot edit or change anything after MIP insertion
D. You can change the timing after the MIP insertion
Answer: A
QUESTION NO: 2
Which compression form is supported by the DCM-G?
A. H.264 HD
B. MPEG-2 HD
C. H.264 SD
D. Jpeg 2000 (j2k)
Answer: A
QUESTION NO: 3
Which of the following products can be used as an encoder and a decoder?
A. D9887B
B. D9094
C. D9093
D. D9894
Answer: B, C
